data.description: Investor alert! Home currently leased to a licensed adult care business. Lease until July 2024, tenant would like to continue lease beyond July 2024. Current lease is 2550 month. 3/2 concrete block stucco with a 2 car side entry garage. Fire sprinkler system throughout house. Inside laundry room, newer slider with built in blinds leads to covered patio AND covered screened in porch, fenced back yard. Guest bath has backyard access door for the buyer who might want a future pool with plenty of space in backyard to build one! Located in Indian Trails in the ''BR'' section, just down the road from the new hospital on north side of town. Within a few miles of shopping, medical, schools and quick 15 min to the beaches.
